description:
With the Minecraft v1.21.5, "Spring To Life" update coming out, we decide to terraform the desert area outside Sandy City. Most of the new blocks released work great in a desert setting so this allows us to check them out in a real application.

We also take some time to explore, collect, and discover how the new blocks work in the game.
